ZH: 这是一份机密文件，只有授权人员可以查看。
EN: This is a confidential document, only authorized personnel can access it.

ZH: 请在箱子上标明“机密”字样。
EN: Please label the box with the word "confidential".

ZH: 公司的财务报告是机密的，不能随便泄露。
EN: The company's financial report is confidential and should not be disclosed casually.

ZH: 我们需要签署一份机密协议，以保护双方的利益。
EN: We need to sign a confidential agreement to protect the interests of both parties.

ZH: 这个会议室是机密讨论的场所，请关闭手机。
EN: This meeting room is for confidential discussions, please turn off your cell phones.

ZH: 你可以放心，这个文件已经被妥善保管，绝不会外泄。
EN: You can rest assured that this document has been properly secured and will not be leaked.

ZH: 请在文件上签字确认，表示你已经阅读并理解了机密性。
EN: Please sign on the document to acknowledge that you have read and understood the confidentiality.

ZH: 所有员工都需要签署保密协议，以保护公司的机密信息。
EN: All employees need to sign a confidentiality agreement to protect the company's confidential information.

ZH: 这个案子还处于机密阶段，不能对外透露任何细节。
EN: This case is still in the confidential stage, no details can be disclosed to the public.

ZH: 我们需要把这个消息保持机密，直到正式公布。
EN: We need to keep this news confidential until it is officially announced.

ZH: 这份报告包含重要的机密数据，需要双重加密才能查看。
EN: This report contains important confidential data that requires double encryption to access.

ZH: 你必须在机密室内使用专用密码才能进入。
EN: You must use a special password to enter the confidential room.

ZH: 这些文件是机密级别的，只能在特定的电脑上查看。
EN: These documents are of confidential level and can only be viewed on specific computers.

ZH: 请确保机密信息不会被无意间传播出去。
EN: Please ensure that confidential information is not inadvertently spread.

ZH: 各部门之间需要建立机密沟通渠道，以确保信息的安全传递。
EN: Confidential communication channels need to be established between departments to ensure secure information transfer.

ZH: 这个文件已经经过机密处理，只有授权人员可以解密。
EN: This document has been confidentially processed and can only be decrypted by authorized personnel.

ZH: 在发邮件时，我们必须注意保护邮件的机密性。
EN: When sending emails, we must pay attention to protecting the confidentiality of the messages.

ZH: 这是一份机密合同，双方必须严格遵守其中约定的保密条款。
EN: This is a confidential contract, and both parties must strictly comply with the confidentiality clauses stated within.

ZH: 请在机密文件上签字，并归还给我。
EN: Please sign on the confidential document and return it to me.

ZH: 这个项目涉及机密技术，我们需要采取额外的安全措施来保护它。
EN: This project involves confidential technology, and we need to take extra security measures to protect it.
